Class SimpleJsonDataStore

All Implemented Interfaces:
net.sf.uadetector.datastore.DataStore
public final class SimpleJsonDataStore
extends net.sf.uadetector.datastore.AbstractDataStore
implements net.sf.uadetector.datastore.DataStore

This is the simplest implementation of a DataStore. It initialize the store by reading the UAS data via the passed URL and store it only in the Java heap space.

The given resource must have a valid JSON format with UTF-8 charset. Every entity must be valid against his own checksum (in SHA-256).

Author:
André Rouél
